h2. How to share resources cross domain

This is a case collection for sharing resources between different domains.

h3. Server Proxy
Server Proxy is using web server to request data from other domain(s) and than provider to self domain,.
JavaScript needn't create a cross-domain HTTP request but just retrieve data from local host.
